“Sure, those all sound good though...oh! We could do, like, split pizzas!”
Split pizzas? Like different topping on each side?
“Exactly!”
“Maybe, we could get each flavor but half the pizzas?”
“Yeah, Yeah, let’s do that!”
Yeah!

Upon hearing this he nods while also seeming to remember something along the lines of drinks. Thus causing them to ask if anyone would like drinks. Before they ask if they can cover the bill. This coming from a place of not seeing them in a while and wanting them to enjoy dining at the pizzaria without having to worry about cost.
“S-Sure! That’s really nice of you to do! As for drinks...how about apple juice for me?”
Eyy, thanks bucci! Lemonade for me!

“Of course, after all it’s only the polite thing to do right? Also remember your manners okay I don’t wanna be kicked out of this place and I doubt you do as well”, he says before turning to Heliotrope and asking if they had any drink requests before they ordered and asked for a table.
